Class View<ViewModelType extends ViewModel>

    public abstract class View<ViewModelType extends ViewModel>
extends Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Abstract class for a MVVMView - you have to say which View Model it uses. Then you can use the embedded ViewModel property which is typed correctly.
